### **Files Created:**

1. **📄 Landing Page** (`index.html`) - Cinematic IMAX-themed homepage
2. **🗃️ Database Interface** (`database.html`) - Interactive theatre browser with dark theme
3. **🐍 Data Validation** (`scripts/validate_data.py`) - Python script for CSV validation
